title: How to Respond to Doubting God and Mental Health with Levi Lusko
description:
Levi Lusko joins us to share his story, talk about his book, and share his viewpoints on mental health and Christian doubters.


Want to send Jeanine a message?  

You can do that here: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy by clicking "Message."
